{"tid":1642492,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【(Juno) kay isn't me】謝安琪討論區(9) - 捨平凡 愛動盪 人人其實有個願望","createTime":"2019-10-09T17:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T12:31:56.000Z","uid":35094,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a84981998de2f5cf769240e33127f8df95a2f3","tid":1642492,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3j8ZfW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3j8ZfW.jpg&h=6913ee3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續吹"},{"pid":"f2e6671729091b9140a517118bf35fc4d3131d36","tid":1642492,"uid":98930,"like":25,"dislike":7,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"個演唱會Fila 贊助，都預咗唔會有家明嗰啲唱啦，肯唱獨家村已經算係咁啦，你見謝安琪都鞠曬躬咁。<br />\n你要明白係呢個時勢唔表態都已經好有勇氣，幾多歌手藝人比中共逼表態愛國，唔支持就玩抵制。<br />\n謝安琪可以發聲支持香港呀，但之後邊個肯/敢出錢投資？ <br />\n有時唔使乜都做到出哂面嘅，大家明咪算囉，我相信佢係愛香港嘅，至少佢冇選擇做護旗手"},{"pid":"25850ad4a446a89115a117941c09ab35c56bd4e4","tid":1642492,"uid":52978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:06:20.000Z","msg":"唔講政治取態，只講個show<br />\n<br />\n唔滿意"},{"pid":"a421dafe8ed5ecb3b0d0bc0fbf75f032da00c801","tid":1642492,"uid":52978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:07:08.000Z","msg":"失望就緊，但去到呢個程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6e34f52e0ddca1e9f7f8cb3a5a9f29984de363","tid":1642492,"uid":114618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:22:50.000Z","msg":"啊！！juno俾返kay我！！！！！<br />\n放過佢啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc25a7b7375328490ca2eab5a9dc598c653946a5","tid":1642492,"uid":225229,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:24:44.000Z","msg":"要光復Kay媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時先比番以前嘅謝安琪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90943d8bca78c0404877947b53fc6e2b9a1f11ad","tid":1642492,"uid":20546,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:26:00.000Z","msg":"真係無預佢有1/3時間係唱juno既歌囉<br />\n睇謝安琪又好浦銘心又好<br />\n<br />\n都唔代表會識juno/董折既歌吧？<br />\n真係聽到o撚哂咀<br />\n<br />\n好失望"},{"pid":"476bf3ef945db43802fcb3b7a88f6b9c9d40fcb5","tid":1642492,"uid":302834,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:34:57.000Z","msg":"雖然今次真係個歌單好唔掂<br />\n但今次睇得出 阿Kay真係狀態好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聲靚唱功好咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果用呢個狀態搞一次真真正正既kay歌演唱會<br />\n一定好好好好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想聽山林道 愁人節 十字架 跟我走 亡命之途 3/8 .........<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3837e0467e71d7d6928bc54ef9f1e240b0e88cc","tid":1642492,"uid":265073,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:35:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDtu9Oa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDtu9Oa.png&h=d475f59c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8b9b0adcf147f2e0555bd7cf06017b9914bba35","tid":1642492,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:12:02.000Z","msg":"做咩有兩個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf539ecb8b234a5ff36248edca2e0ce842a9f32","tid":1642492,"uid":194180,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:57:03.000Z","msg":"08年聽Kay，唔算係忠粉，但所有side track兼2隻國語碟都聽到熟<br />\n<br />\n同大家一樣睇完好失望。知你係浦銘心，知你要玩藝術，你要四不做都算...<br />\n<br />\n個問題係 謝安琪你呃尻左自己歌迷呀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訪問又話搵緊嘉賓，又話係自己想做既類型，仲要吹到用三個月好用心咁諗歌單?! <br />\n<br />\n諗住實係因為用心姐身分唱Kay歌所以要用心度，但end up原來係用左3個月同麥生爭要有幾多首Kay歌，可能本身係一首都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事先講明玩翻唱咪算囉，又要喺d訪問亂咁吹<br />\n<br />\n好彩無買到件tshirt，唔係實即場撕撚爛佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdf365f05ca633b94a0751c1f6a2bb5b3cce234","tid":1642492,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:38:41.000Z","msg":"定名為《kay isn&rsquo;t me. Live》，今次演唱會其實包含了屬於謝安琪的部份，也有一個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大篇幅是有關虛構角色「浦銘心」</span></strong>，當中更會補完一些唱片未提及的情節，屆時樂迷可以自行找出彩蛋，串連起MV中的故事。Juno分享：「由《勇悍‧17》開始，我哋已經架空咗一個世界，例如創作浦銘心嘅時候，佢嘅背景好神秘，有人覺得佢無父無母，永遠都係一個人。因為我哋想探討，背離傳統儒家思想，離開既定人生軌跡嘅生命。」所謂「離經叛道」，始終是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Juno創作的命題</span></strong>，難怪今次演唱會，也要是一個不一樣的紅館騷。又可以透露一下，除了Kay的演出外，今次演唱會也加插了不少Juno特意拍攝的映畫，令觀眾更容易導入是次主題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9C%BE%E6%A8%82%E8%BF%B7/383139/%E8%AC%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%90%AA%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83-%E9%80%86%E8%BD%89%E7%B4%85%E9%A4%A8%E6%80%9D%E7%B6%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%97%A2%E5%AE%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%A1%86%E6%AD%BB-%E6%9C%89%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E4%BD%86%E5%81%9A%E5%BE%97%E7%88%BD?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=01pplmusic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25BF%25B7%2F383139%2F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%2590%25AA%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2594%25B1%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2580%2586%25E8%25BD%2589%25E7%25B4%2585%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E6%2580%259D%25E7%25B6%25AD-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2597%25A2%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%25A1%2586%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B%25E4%25BD%2586%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%25BE%2597%25E7%2588%25BD%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3D01pplmusic&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX50trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=6f8cc578\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9C%BE%E6%A8%82%E8%BF%B7/383139/%E8%AC%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%90%AA%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83-%E9%80%86%E8%BD%89%E7%B4%85%E9%A4%A8%E6%80%9D%E7%B6%AD-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%97%A2%E5%AE%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%A1%86%E6%AD%BB-%E6%9C%89%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E4%BD%86%E5%81%9A%E5%BE%97%E7%88%BD?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=01pplmusic</a>"},{"pid":"215ac9fc868ccc59d5ea6ec9e8f0bbcd10989f2b","tid":1642492,"uid":251458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T23:06:37.000Z","msg":"星期五$680<br />\n係咪應該放番出去？<br />\n利申：愁人節時期仲係中學生就fans<br />\n<br />\n一直當拾回係last一個concert<br />\n情願佢好似彭羚咁永遠唔出黎<br />\n係我心目中留下最完美既印象<br />\n<br />\n一直唔明點解咁中二病，<br />\n改個名蒲銘心<br />\n而家明白了<br />\n就係<br />\nkay已經過去了，<br />\n而家呢個只係代唱角色！<br />\n真正的謝安琪永遠只係係2014."},{"pid":"f75c86d676870dd300eee6dabdaff00c928fa256","tid":1642492,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:09:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1642488\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1642488</a><br />\n<br />\n人多d 去呢到"},{"pid":"16b002cf4664aa0abead86991889bf477693a211","tid":1642492,"uid":75329,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T02:38:01.000Z","msg":"你話論作為一份藝術作品，我覺得佢贏曬香港咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然真係唱咗好多juno，唱到我自己都以為係佢新歌嚟，<br />\n其實佢都一早講過話係佢自己揀，何不改變心態理解下佢所揀俾大家既嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少尋晚我聽到獨家村係流曬眼淚，到依家呢一秒都係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係想大家一定要撐，至少唔好屌到佢之後都唔出返嚟<br />\n<br />\nbtw 尋晚唱功好過雞容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3633906450df8647b0